*The Civilians' dialogue mentions that they get their Death runes from the [[Dwarf|dwarves]] who dig them out from the [[Underground Pass (dungeon)|Underground Pass]]. This may be a reference to the fact that the [[Death Altar]] is located just beyond the Underground Pass.

